      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that's ready to hit the road? This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a great opportunity to own a dependable car at a fantastic price! It shows some honest signs of use and character from its years of service, but it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone needing a hardworking ride. Come see why this well-loved vehicle still has plenty of miles left to offer!",
