    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total gem? I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a stunner. I've babied this car from day one\u2014always garaged, strictly hand-washed, and the interior is so clean it still feels brand new. It drives like an absolute dream and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you want a ride that\u2019s been loved and looked after, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis represents a pinnacle of Japanese engineering, featuring a numbers-matching 13B-REW rotary engine with exceptional compression and a perfectly synchronized sequential twin-turbocharger system. The powertrain is mated to a crisp five-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, utilizing aluminum double-wishbones to maintain a perfect 50:50 weight distribution. Mechanically pristine, this example shows no signs of thermal degradation or vacuum system fatigue, offering a pure, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare in the modern market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. One owner. No accidents. Clean title. Serviced regularly.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector's dream, maintained in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero swirls, chips, or imperfections, having been exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records from authorized dealerships. With incredibly low mileage and a chassis that has never seen inclement weather, it drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new vehicle. This is an uncompromising example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
