      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in an impeccable state, reflecting a history of fastidious maintenance and climate-controlled storage. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, adheres to the most rigorous standards of preservation. For the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in true showroom condition. We invite serious inquiries to experience this masterfully maintained example in person.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
